Subject: Secunia Research: uTorrent / BitTorrent Web UI HTTP "Range" Header DoS

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 11/06/2008

        - uTorrent / BitTorrent Web UI HTTP "Range" Header DoS -

====================================================================== 
